headline: FOX News Digital Overtakes CNN With Total Digital Multiplatform Unique Visitors in October
summary: NEW YORK, November 21, 2024--FOX News Digital finished October delivering year-over-year growth, overtaking CNN with total digital multiplatform unique visitors for the third time this year, according to Comscore.
